scenes.description: AZKi, Tokino Sora, and Sakura Miko discuss the previous quiz result as a correct image of many Ankimo characters is shown.
AZKi explains that one different Ankimo was mixed into the Halloween-themed ones, and the group talks about how easy or hard it was.
Tokino Sora takes her turn to present a Chromakey quiz, asking the others what a certain group of Hololive members have in common.
A visual quiz plays with rotating icons of various Hololive members. AZKi and Miko try to guess the common theme.
Tokino Sora reveals the answer: all the members shown have birthdays in October. AZKi and Miko react to getting it right.
Sakura Miko prepares to present her quiz, which involves identifying a Hololive member from a close-up image.
A highly zoomed-in, rotating image of a character's thigh and skirt is shown as the quiz. Sora and AZKi struggle and then guess.
The answer is revealed to be Hoshimachi Suisei. AZKi explains how she knew, leading to a playful discussion about her observation skills.
Tokino Sora suggests doing one more round with increased difficulty, and the others agree, noting the previous spike in difficulty.
